ARM: dts: DRA72: switch to cpsw slave0 for ethernet

On DRA72 EVM, cpsw slave1 is muxed with VIN2A, hence switch to cpsw
slave0 for ethernet. Add gpio hog entry to pcf_gpio_21 in order to
select cpsw slave0.

